					"metaDescription": "Eighty-eight percent of IT leaders are actively consolidating and optimizing their technology stacks. Platform consolidation — the integration of multiple tools and infrastructure into a single, cohesive platform — is a strategic priority for security and IT leaders, driven by increasing tech stack complexity and economic challenges. Unfortunately, platform consolidation projects often struggle to meet expectations due to gaps between what platforms can do and what it should do.",
