						"title": "2024 API Security and Management Report",
						"titleSize": null,
						"subtitle": "Benchmark the security risks, performance, and management of API endpoints",
						"subtitleSize": null,
						"copy": "Today, APIs outpace other Internet traffic, comprising 57% of the dynamic Internet traffic processed by Cloudflare. However, APIs are also increasingly complex to manage and protect against abuse.\n\nBased on aggregated traffic patterns observed by Cloudflare's global network, the 2024 API Security and Management Report explores:\n\n<span style=\"color: #ff6633;\">&#10004;</span> The growing risk of shadow APIs<br/>\n<span style=\"color: #ff6633;\">&#10004;</span> The most common API errors and threats towards APIs<br/>\n<span style=\"color: #ff6633;\">&#10004;</span> Global API usage across different industries<br/>\n<span style=\"color: #ff6633;\">&#10004;</span> Predictions and recommendations for holistically protecting APIs\n",
